        "In `goseg/broadcast/broadcast.go`, `BroadcastToClients` executes `GetStateJson` and calls `auth.ClientManager.BroadcastAuth(authJson)` before checking `err`, and then calls it again on the success path, creating inconsistent observable outcomes for the same API call.",
        "`goseg/system/system.go` exposes telemetry APIs with mixed error contracts (`GetCPU`, `GetMemory`, `GetDisk` return errors, while `GetTemp` returns only `float64` and logs/returns `0` on failure), and this diverges from the same package's public resource-status surface."
